育行政部门，由上级教育行政部门督办问责。 据介绍，近年来，各地不断提升依法治教、规范办学水平，但部分地方和学校违规办学问题依然突出，严重影响学生身心健康，破坏良好教育生态，群众反映强烈，社会高度关注。教育部基础教育「规范管理年」行动，将进一步清理整治基础教育领域存在的违法违规、违背教育规律和教育功利化短视化行为，进一步建立健全依法管理、从严管理、规范管理的长效机制。整治挤占「课间十分钟」 纵容校园霸凌等 教育部出手了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ad9bf9e978eef45dd0fe1d5c93f0485_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655960473"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI9cG45a75lKsOEAMaCTEwODA0NjgzMSC3vIuyBjAAOMMBQCpyCTY1NTk2MDQ3M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1715695695.979518", "card_id": "Q_651356900", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "猫咪不喜欢被人摸「脚」，有什么原因？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-639ec31134fa287a23cb46bf84cc9eab_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651356900"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9cG45a75lKsOEAMaCTEwNzAyMzg0NSCewa+wBjAAOCBAK3IJNjUxMzU2OTAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1715695695.980089", "card_id": "Q_655415475", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 61}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "与上司意见不合时，我该怎么做？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-773a141da63e6ee797a2ac183df23e6e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655415475"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9cG45a75lKsOEAMaCTEwNzkyNTQ4OCC